---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer
    class="border-t border-anime-dark/10 dark:border-white/5 bg-white dark:bg-[#121212] py-12 transition-colors duration-500"
>
    <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
            <div class="md:col-span-1">
                <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 group">
                    <span
                        class="text-xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight text-anime-dark dark:text-white group-hover:text-anime-pink transition-colors"
                    >
                        ANIME<span class="text-anime-blue">.LOG</span>
                    </span>
                </a>
                <p
                    class="mt-4 text-anime-dark/60 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm max-w-xs leading-relaxed font-medium"
                >
                    喜欢把日常写成微光，把思绪折成风。<br
                    />愿在时光里慢慢生长，与你不期而遇。
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-2 flex md:justify-end items-center">
                <div class="text-right">
                    <h3
                        class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 text-anime-dark dark:text-white"
                    >
                        追踪
                    </h3>
                    <ul
                        class="flex gap-6 text-sm text-anime-dark/70 dark:text-gray-400"
                    >
                        <li>
                            <a
                                href="https://github.com"
                                target="_blank"
                                class="hover:text-anime-pink dark:hover:text-anime-pink transition-colors"
                                >GitHub</a
                            >
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a
                                href="#"
                                class="hover:text-anime-pink dark:hover:text-anime-pink transition-colors"
                                >小红书</a
                            >
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a
                                href="/rss.xml"
                                class="hover:text-anime-pink dark:hover:text-anime-pink transition-colors"
                                >RSS 订阅</a
                            >
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-anime-dark/5 dark:border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center text-xs text-anime-dark/40 dark:text-gray-600 gap-4 font-mono"
        >
            <p>&copy; {today.getFullYear()} Suxinnai. 保留所有权利。</p>
            <div class="flex space-x-6">
                <a
                    href="/privacy"
                    class="hover:text-anime-dark dark:hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors"
                    >隐私政策</a
                >
                <a
                    href="/terms"
                    class="hover:text-anime-dark dark:hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors"
                    >使用条款</a
                >
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
